posting_body: ['Property Address', '1299 Grand Ave - 106 | St. Paul, MN 55105', 'Available:', '09/01/2022', 'Offered By', 'At Home Apartments', 'Description', 'Large Back Corner 1 BR at Grand Heritage Apartments', 'This spacious, first-floor back corner one-bedroom apartment has updated kitchen cabinets, along with white granite countertops and pot racks for additional storage.', 'Additionally, the bathroom has been fully renovated with a subway tile surround in the shower and stylish fixtures throughout.', 'Bordering the Summit Hill and Mac-Groveland neighborhoods of St. Paul, the Grand Heritage Apartments boasts historic charm combined with beautiful, contemporary updates, making modern living more convenient.', "Just a short walk from a plethora of savory restaurants and charming boutiques, and next door to the famous Kowalski's Market, you are sure to feel At Home on Grand Avenue!", 'Call us at', 'show contact info', 'or visit us at <URL> for more information and tour options.', 'Photos are a representation of the property and may not be of the exact apartment.', '**$150 Administration Fee added to lease.', 'Pet fees/restrictions may apply.', 'Please inquire about your specific pet.', '**', 'Amenities', 'Convenient Coinless Laundry', 'Fitness Center and Clubhouse Across the Street', '24-Hour Emergency Maintenance', 'Secured Entryways', 'Online Resident Portal - Rent Payments and Maintenance Requests', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 1BD/1.0BA', 'Square Feet: 800', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $1,066.00', 'Available:', '09/01/2022', 'Application Fee: $55.00', 'Security Deposit: $600.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs not allowed']
